    description= _ ""At an island northwest of Wesnoth, a group of drakes had been living without much trouble although battling with Nages was as usual. However, when an unexpected visitor came down to the island, those drakes were in trouble seriously. 
Brave drakes flew away to save their home.

This is playable all scenarios (12 playable and an epilogue), but still an early release, so bugs possible and some scenarios require further balancing. The feed back will be great appreciation.

Brave Wings, version 0.7.0
Required Wesnoth version: 1.8.0 or higher""

